$ The Farm Puzzle 
$
$ A farmer has 7 animals on his farm: pigs and hens.
$ They all together have 22 legs. How many pigs and how many
$ hens does the farmer have?
$

language ESSENCE' 1.b.a

letting numberOfLegs be 22
letting FEET be domain int(2,4)
find a1,a2,a3,a4,a5,a6,a7 : FEET 

such that
     a1 + a2 + a3 + a4 + a5 + a6 + a7 = numberOfLegs 
